1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:09,651
Chapter 1 Believe You Can Succeed and You Will Success means many wonderful, positive things.

2
00:00:09,921 --> 00:00:20,610
Success means personal prosperity, a fine home, vacations, travel, new things, financial security, giving your children maximum advantages.

3
00:00:21,040 --> 00:00:28,691
Success means winning admiration, leadership, being looked up to by people in your business and social life.

4
00:00:29,040 --> 00:00:34,691
Success means freedom, freedom from worries, fears, frustrations, and failure.

5
00:00:34,961 --> 00:00:42,051
Success means self-respect, continually finding more real happiness and satisfaction from life,

6
00:00:42,241 --> 00:00:45,251
being able to do more for those who depend on you.

7
00:00:45,601 --> 00:00:47,731
Success means winning.

8
00:00:48,001 --> 00:00:51,651
Success, achievement, is the goal of life.

9
00:00:52,001 --> 00:00:54,371
Every human being wants success.

10
00:00:54,561 --> 00:00:57,731
Everybody wants the best this life can deliver.

11
00:00:58,001 --> 00:01:01,331
Nobody enjoys crawling, living in mediocrity.

12
00:01:01,601 --> 00:01:06,131
No one likes feeling second class and feeling forced to go that way.

